{"tid":740729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵承認：紅磡站北面隧道牆壁部份鋼筋並無扭入螺絲頭","createTime":"2018-07-13T06:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T08:20:16.000Z","uid":31314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6737dbb1f8f7e6ca60076a61e4ed2674e38cb7","tid":740729,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中綫土木工程總經理黃智聰在立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會特別會議上承認，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>早前出現滲水的紅磡站北面隧道，牆壁部份鋼筋並無扭入螺絲頭，部分螺絲頭的保護蓋未有拆除。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋關注，涉事工程由誰監督及負責，黃智聰指，手上無相關資料，但承認港鐵在工程監督有所不足，會檢討事件，如果有同事沒有跟隨程序，港鐵會跟進。<br />\n<br />\n中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻表示，去年9月18日和禮頓高層會面後，禮頓接受糾正鋼筋的方法，但要求自行和港鐵交涉，中科為解決事件，同意刪除交給禮頓的相片和影片，並向運輸及房屋局發電郵指，有關沙中綫的問題已解決，並接受所有工程資料不能向外透露。<br />\n<br />\n潘焯鴻又說，當時刪除了部分相關相片，但仍然保留80GB的相片和資料，已經交執法部門跟進。"},{"pid":"0b08874a49fe2c211b289fe4056820efbddcda33","tid":740729,"uid":151496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"80GB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aaeb82fad8e3c0d66a487a949db6667c4109069","tid":740729,"uid":117602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b08874a49fe2c211b289fe4056820efbddcda33","tid":740729,"uid":151496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"80GB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"可能係片"},{"pid":"d55b9e3b34219b7ca264358f7183966def998960","tid":740729,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aaeb82fad8e3c0d66a487a949db6667c4109069","tid":740729,"uid":117602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b08874a49fe2c211b289fe4056820efbdd